		<title>不打掃還幫倒忙！黑狗愛上「掃把刷背」畫面混亂又有趣 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/28/%e4%b8%8d%e6%89%93%e6%8e%83%e9%82%84%e5%b9%ab%e5%80%92%e5%bf%99%ef%bc%81%e9%bb%91%e7%8b%97%e6%84%9b%e4%b8%8a%e3%80%8c%e6%8e%83%e6%8a%8a%e5%88%b7%e8%83%8c%e3%80%8d%e7%95%ab%e9%9d%a2%e6%b7%b7%e4%ba%82/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
